 ('15', '15', 'en_us', 'Justin Golmer', NULL, '#ffae96', 'Photography Promo', '<p class=\"large\">Justin Gollmer, one of our go-to photography partners, asked us design a ten-year retrospective promotional brochure. Wake, Style, Shoot, Do It All Again is a collection of images highlighting his work behind, beside, and around the camera. The brochure is divided into four sections that blur the lines between Gollmer’s personal and commercial work: people, action, travel, and product. Short sheets bound to the exterior provide thumbnail image guides to each section with captions for each image.</p>', 'Wake up\r\nStyle\r\nshoot\r\ndo it all\r\nagain', '[{\"col1\":\"Recogonition\",\"col2\":\"Print Regional Design Annual 2015\"}]', '#efefef', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-13 20:39:13', '2016-11-22 21:55:01', 'fe590c8b-e0d5-40e6-ac69-88bce93b6fb0'),
 ('16', '16', 'en_us', 'Oiselle', NULL, '#ff5822', 'Brand Identity System', '<p class=\"large\">As they prepared to open their first bricks and mortar store, Oiselle&mdash;a pioneer in women’s running and athletic fashion&mdash;had a mature brand that needed an infusion of new energy. Turnstyle worked with the Oiselle team to establish an updated identity system and then applied it to a huge range of customer touch points, coordinated to deliver, install and deploy in concert with their store opening in Seattle’s University Village in the summer of 2015.</p>', 'AN\r\nINFUSION\r\nOF\r\nNEW\r\nENERGY', NULL, '#efefef', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-13 20:39:34', '2016-11-15 23:10:25', '0e3ab165-2609-406e-ad14-35ee38513a67'),
