 ('209', '101', '10', '1', 'en_us', '11', '', '{\"typeId\":\"11\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Studio\",\"slug\":\"studio\",\"postDate\":1478129954,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"48\":{\"102\":{\"type\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"backgroundImage\":[\"97\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"linkUrl\":\"\\/contact\",\"header\":\"Drop \\r\\nus \\r\\na \\r\\nline\",\"subtext\":\"Contact Us\",\"fontColor\":\"#000000\"}}},\"45\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\">Born in 2004<\\/p>\",\"46\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\">We are a full-service creative agency with offices in Seattle and Portland. A dedicated team of designers, strategists, developers and account specialists, we create highly-crafted brand experiences that clarify purpose, encourage action, and inspire brand loyalty. We\\u2019d love to get to know you and help tell your story.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"10\":{\"103\":{\"type\":\"carousel\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"images\":[\"48\",\"49\",\"50\"],\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-2\"}},\"104\":{\"type\":\"twoColumnContent\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"leftColumn\":\"<p class=\\\"h3 med\\\">STYLE<br>IS A<br>SIMPLE<br>WAY<br>OF<br>SAYING<br>COMPLEX<br>THINGS<br><span class=\\\"blue\\\">&mdash;JEAN<br>COCTEAU<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"rightColumn\":\"<p><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/turnstyle.studio\\/_ui\\/img\\/work\\/t-1.svg#asset:60:url\\\"><\\/p>\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-1\"}},\"105\":{\"type\":\"twoColumnContent\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"leftColumn\":\"<p>Style is Not a&nbsp;<br>4-letter Word<\\/p>\",\"rightColumn\":\"<p>In our experience, the brands that are the most magnetic are those which project distinct, memorable and charismatic personalities. These brands place equal emphasis on what they say and how they say it. Some design purists might say that style is merely artificial decoration that should be avoided in favor of logic&mdash;\\u201cform fol