say it. Some design purists might say that style is merely artificial decoration that should be avoided in favor of logic&mdash;\\u201cform follows function\\u201d and all that. Don\\u2019t get us wrong, we\\u2019re not proponents of style for its own sake, or as ornament applied after an idea has already been defined. Rather, we employ style as an integral and strategic component of our brand-development process. At its best, style can be that magical something about a company or product that pulls people in and transcends the logical. So, to us, style is not a 4-letter word. On the contrary, we embrace it, harnessing its power to cut through the clutter.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p class=\\\"large\\\"><span class=\\\"white\\\">And besides, \\u201cstyle\\u201d has five letters.<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-2\"}},\"106\":{\"type\":\"twoColumnContent\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"leftColumn\":\"<p class=\\\"large\\\"><span class=\\\"white\\\">We Do<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"rightColumn\":\"<p class=\\\"h2 caps\\\"><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/turnstyle.studio\\/strategy#entry:55\\\">Strategy<\\/a><br><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/turnstyle.studio\\/identity#entry:56\\\">Identity<\\/a><br>Digital<br>Print<br>Packaging<br>Environment<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-2\"}},\"107\":{\"type\":\"twoColumnContent\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"leftColumn\":\"<p class=\\\"h3 caps\\\">our<br>clients<br>&<br>industries<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p class=\\\"h3 caps\\\"><\\/p>\",\"rightColumn\":\"\",\"verticalSpacingLevel\":\"vertical-spacing-1\"}},\"108\":{\"type\":\"twoColumnContent\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"leftColumn\":\"<p><span class=\\\"gray\\\">Industry<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p class=\\\"h3 caps\\\">teague<br>nike<br>starbucks<br>microsoft<br>amazon<br>aiga<br>nordstrom<br>teague<br>nike<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n